Package: AfriAtlas
Title: An R Package for Automating the Visualization of African Bird Atlas Project Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bello", family = "Adamu Danmallam", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "adamubello001@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7783-4351"))
Description: Provides tools for generating standardized species distribution maps 
    and survey coverage (effort) maps using the African Bird Atlas Project (ABAP) API. 
    The package includes functions for visualizing pentad-level sighting data and 
    survey effort across African countries. It relies on 'sf' for spatial handling, 
    and 'ggplot2' and 'rnaturalearth' for high-quality cartographic visualization.
